<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3154556" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="9">This tool is used to rotate the object. It corresponds to the command <emph>Rotate</emph> found on the $[officename] Draw Main toolbar under <emph>Effects</emph>.</paragraph>
